{"tid":762391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【入黎講下煮麵食開邊隻牌子,同埋會落咩餸】","createTime":"2018-07-31T08:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T14:20:05.000Z","uid":119688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c0fe9aa52647f59492bc011c91fc16cc51106902","tid":762391,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 簡簡單單又黎煮個麵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入黎講低 食開咩麵,配咩餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身鐘意麵質好,唔易碎 <br />\n泡菜國呢方面就無得輸<br />\n辣雞麵/芝士麵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時無菜就唔落菜 食肉獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貢丸/牛丸/肥牛<br />\n仲有最愛既菠菜丸同芝士腸啊屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地又會點樣揀呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914c77d11e218bccba7ca8f984e81fdc5a3b4fce","tid":762391,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f9118ec5ee59430e4be3e5326af7d12b4976b8","tid":762391,"uid":189336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:49:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0570fa88ef59264beef87575cf96ca7ab7e17f7","tid":762391,"uid":16934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T08:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/165036_7d7374c48df911b24949597c6ab08707.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2